OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fsunny spells to end the day. Another
OL,7,Fwarm night for many, especially in
OL,8,Furban areas, with cooler conditions in
OL,9,Frural locations. Dry with light winds
OL,10,Fand cloudy periods, some fog may
OL,11,Fdevelop in places by dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAnother very warm day, dry and
OL,14,Fpredominantly sunny, the sunshine may
OL,15,Fturn hazy at times with the passage of
OL,16,Fhigh-level cloud. Cooler along coastal
OL,17,Fareas, with an onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
