OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FCloudier and cooler on Saturday with
OL,7,Fshowers later. Cloudy periods
OL,8,Fthroughout Sunday, though brightening
OL,9,Fin the afternoon. Returning to dry and
OL,10,Flargely sunny conditions by Monday.
OL,11,FTemperatures around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
